PENDER COUNTY, et al.
v.
SULLIVAN 14P18-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 5, 2018 Donald Sullivan, Marion P. Sullivan, for Sullivan, Donald, et al. Robert H. Corbett, Attorney at Law, Burgaw, for Pender County, et al.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 5th of March 2018 by Defendant to Withdraw Appeal:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of April 2018."
